data.description: BEAUTIFUL and "Hard to Find" luxurious single story home at the end of a Cul-de-Sac with an oversized driveway. This magnificent residence is located behind the highly desirable Gated Community of The Cove in Southern Highlands and boasts a bright and open floor plan and endless upgrades including a stylish kitchen with pantry & huge island that opens to the family room which is perfect for entertaining. French Glass backdoors sliders open to a private coved Patio. Bedrooms on Separate ends of the home. Large primary bedroom with an incredible en-suite bathroom and custom walk in shower with rain shower head. Surrounded by other one story homes and 50-60 yards from the resort-style community pool plus playground - this property has it all and is an absolute MUST SEE!
